name: Frencho Retro Meme
description: This is a collab piece using the well known french photogropher Robert Doisneau and one of his wide spread photographs along with K.C. Green and his creation of Dick butt to mould the two to enable a representation of digital art in 2021 24-bit color image (8 bits x 3 channels)  For more on this artist see @_Shmeel on Twitter
